Above the text there is a religious cross in rose gold. Except the occasion "Confirmation", that is also in rose gold, all text can be personalized and has a color similar to the rose gold frame.

The vintage, ornate frame is based on an antique French book cover binding, by Georges Mercier (1885-1939) – Madame de Maupin by Theophile Gautier, edition 1911, now in the public domain. Price:$2.00
